spec_data.Name: python2-rows
spec_data.Description:
No matter in which format your tabular data is: rows will import it,
automatically detect types and give you high-level Python objects so
you can start working with the data instead of trying to parse it. It
is also locale-and-unicode aware.

Python 2 version.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 03:43:47 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A common, beautiful interface to tabular data, no matter the format
